    videoPlayerGeometry.firstMaterial?.diffuse.contents = skScene

or:

    videoPlayerGeometry.firstMaterial?.diffuse.contents = avPlayer

Here are possible candidates for `.contents` instance property:

 - NSColor / UIColor / CGColor
 - NSNumber
 - NSImage / UIImage / CGImage
 - NSString or NSURL object in AVPlayer
 - CALayer
 - SKTexture / MDLTexture / MTLTexture
 - SpriteKit scene
 - A cube map of specially formatted array of six images

You also missed **`/watch?v=`** in your web address:

    let playerVars: [String: Any] = [ &quot;controls&quot; : 1,
